Class Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sers.webutils.model.BaseEntity
      • org.pahappa.systems.core.models.task.Task
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.sers.webutils.model.Auditable
    @Entity
public class Task
extends org.sers.webutils.model.BaseEntity
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a task entity in the system. Each task is associated with a company, assigned user, and has various attributes such as priority, status, and due date.
